name: Oceania online MMO
blurb: Oceania - MMORPG for PC. Is a beautiful, open-world 3D. You can create new realms on your own and add custom artifacts to the game.

rewards.reward: Participation in the beta testing. Access to the private forum / discussion where you can learn about everything that was happening during the development and share your thoughts and suggestions.
FREE COPY of the game's release for PC and our thanks for your interest in our game

WALLPAPER SET                      \r\nEverything above plus wallpaper set. A large collection of Oceania wallpapers for your PC, Mac, tablet, along with our heartfelt thanks. We appreciate your contribution!

Premium account for 3 months\r\nEverything above plus 3 months of premium access for your account. Having the premium a character upgrades and develops 2 times faster, \r\nmore things fall from monsters. The character gets other  substantial bonuses. Plus everything above.
Soundtracks for the game + unused tracks \r\nEverything above plus all the soundtracks for the game - used and unused.
T-shirt with logo / picture of the game. Free shipping. Plus everything above.
Pet\r\nYou get a pet which will follow you everywhere, take part in battles, obey and help you in any way. Plus everything above.

Own island\r\nAt the beginning of the game you get your own island in the ocean, where you can rule as you wish, you can decorate it, build a tavern, a farm, a livestock or whatever you want.
